{"tid":1553901,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日帶咗個喇叭仔去播《願榮光歸香港》","createTime":"2019-09-08T18:16:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T08:39:03.000Z","uid":33875,"like":89,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"18d752dfe8ee632baa44a283e5cc072a0c49434e","tid":1553901,"uid":33875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T18:16:29.000Z","msg":"第一次聽到呢首歌既大合唱，嗰一刻即刻變咗溫兆倫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為唔想阻到大家叫口號，只係揀中間靜止既時候播<br />\n頭幾次播大家都係默默地聽歌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n播多幾次，開始有人用電話睇歌詞，又有人唔知係邊到攞張貓紙出嚟<br />\n不過大家都係輕哼幾句 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後應該去到律政中心，突然走咗個手足企咗係我身邊一唱齊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n直至唱到：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">捍自由 來齊集這裡 來全力抗對<br />\n勇氣 智慧 也 永不滅</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">手足嗌：「唱大聲啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n全場立即合唱最尾嗰段，再叫幾次「光復香港，時代革命」 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家衝破咗內心關口，落山前跟住唱多幾次，嗰種震撼真係好難忘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者有一日大家都會衝破打狗救人既內心關口 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後誠邀大家，下星期二有國際足球賽事（香港 對 伊朗），希望大家可以入場或係場外唱歌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">9月10日 (星期二) 8:00 PM ＠ 香港大球場</span></strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y7yRDOLCy4Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dy7yRDOLCy4Y&d=h%2B0F1AfFk4MBaO73S6qK%2BpKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=9ebf7456\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y7yRDOLCy4Y</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>何以 這土地 淚再流<br />\n何以 令眾人 亦憤恨<br />\n昂首 拒默沉 吶喊聲 響透<br />\n盼自由 歸於 這裡<br />\n<br />\n何以 這恐懼 抹不走<br />\n何以 為信念 從沒退後<br />\n何解 血在流 但邁進聲 響透<br />\n建自由 光輝 香港<br />\n<br />\n在 晚星 墜落 徬徨 午夜<br />\n迷霧裡 最遠處 吹 來 號 角 聲<br />\n捍自由 來齊集這裡 來全力抗對<br />\n勇氣 智慧 也 永不滅<br />\n<br />\n黎明來到 要光復 這香港<br />\n同行兒女 為正義 時代革命 <br />\n祈求 民主 與自由 萬世都 不朽<br />\n我願 榮光 歸香港</strong></span>"},{"pid":"2f882bed57d1fe9f695bcad7e2986557e9de63c2","tid":1553901,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T18:19:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dab8f17b897da243ea699ed69288b3a496bf2079","tid":1553901,"uid":251769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T18:21:29.000Z","msg":"[急!!!]9/9有班中學生等緊你地救！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1553800\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1553800</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e2f40ccf15d92381c5ceecf61e224eb3007ab6d2","tid":1553901,"uid":33875,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T18:21:56.000Z","msg":"9月10日 (星期二) 8:00 PM ＠ 香港大球場，唱大聲啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf6570589aa558f98ff2ed5d95f1c3f4c17e521f","tid":1553901,"uid":210254,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T18:23:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a0672c9a86a699d3a0829eae498dedb9774a82e","tid":1553901,"uid":52658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T18:24:34.000Z","msg":"我今朝係第一次聽<br />\n係幾好聽幾震憤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5d89b2251da80d0c84b8a613530dd031f58465b","tid":1553901,"uid":33875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf6570589aa558f98ff2ed5d95f1c3f4c17e521f","tid":1553901,"uid":210254,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T18:23:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T18:27:42.000Z","msg":"通常唱完就嗌一陣「光復香港，時代革命」，同埋今日山上路口好多狗，行過又屌一陣狗，唔易搵機會播 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以後既和理非遊行集會再唱過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n勇武既就玩返敲擊樂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef71d262d9383c2ef7f5f6b28a9fa6bb331fa138","tid":1553901,"uid":27597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T18:29:50.000Z","msg":"我諗果個唔算喇叭仔了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75fc46a09a8db38a36f1f46bf2dc0e5c351c7a04","tid":1553901,"uid":251366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T18:32:27.000Z","msg":"星期二入場再唱多次啦"},{"pid":"9b55742fc64c3129b390a54fda3ce82b53220b99","tid":1553901,"uid":33875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T18:33:24.000Z","msg":"幫手填填民間記者會問卷調查<br />\n<br />